      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个完整的yggdrasil消息流转时序图，核心场景是server通过broker下发echo指令，最终由workerEcho处理并返回结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "server",
